The Pantheon way

One thing I’ve noticed is that your instinct is often to ask:

“What operator hides underneath this word?”

For example:

Luck

↓

Preparedness × Optionality × Exposure × Variance

Magic

↓

Unknown operator

Charisma

↓

Attention × Trust × Emotion × Narrative

Leadership

↓

Coordination × Incentives × Vision

That’s a productive habit because it pushes beyond labels toward mechanisms.

